10#include "ipf.h"
11
12void
13alist_free(hosts)
14 alist_t *hosts;
15{
16 alist_t *a, *next;
17
18 for (a = hosts; a != NULL; a = next) {
19 next = a->al_next;
20 free(a);
21 }
22}
